SEARCH
Package gw.plugin.contact

Interface InsuranceCompanySearchPlugin

All Superinterfaces:
InternalPlugin, Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
DemoInsuranceCompanySearchPlugin
public interface InsuranceCompanySearchPlugin extends InternalPlugin

Plugin interface for searching Insurance Company. Specifies an application interface to the remote insurance company management system which can be used to search and retrieve.

Since:
ClaimCenter 50.5

  • Method Details

    • searchByOfficialID

      ContactSearchResult searchByOfficialID(OfficialIDType officialIDType, String officialIDValue, Jurisdiction jurisdiction)
      Searches the insurance company using the official id. Note that the Contacts contained in the ContactSearchResult may not be complete contacts, for performance reasons, they may be just enough data for a user to select a contact from the set of search results. For example, OfficialIDs array is not available in the search results.
      Parameters:
      officialIDType - Required
      officialIDValue - Required
      jurisdiction - Optional search condition
      Returns:
      The search result, mostly single result if there's no duplicated officialID

    • searchByOfficialIDType

      ContactSearchResult searchByOfficialIDType(OfficialIDType officialIDType, Jurisdiction jurisdiction)
      Searches the insurance company using the official id type. It returns all insurance companies with given id type. Note that the Contacts contained in the ContactSearchResult may not be complete contacts, for performance reasons, they may be just enough data for a user to select a contact from the set of search results. For example, OfficialIDs array is not available in the search results.
      Parameters:
      officialIDType - Required
      jurisdiction - Optional search condition
      Returns:
      The search result

    • searchByTag

      ContactSearchResult searchByTag(ContactTagType tagType, OfficialIDType officialIDType, Jurisdiction jurisdiction)
      Searches the insurance company using the tag. It is possible to filter the result by official ID type. Note that the Contacts contained in the ContactSearchResult may not be complete contacts, for performance reasons, they may be just enough data for a user to select a contact from the set of search results. For example, OfficialIDs array is not available in the search results.
      Parameters:
      tagType - Required
      officialIDType - Optional search condition
      jurisdiction - Optional search condition
      Returns:
      The search result

    • retrieveInsuranceCompany

      InsuranceCompany retrieveInsuranceCompany(OfficialIDType officialIDType, String officialIDValue, Jurisdiction jurisdiction)
      Retrieve the insurance company entity using the official id type and id value. The result should be only one by given parameter combination, otherwise IllegalArgumentException will occur.
      Parameters:
      officialIDType - Required
      officialIDValue - Required
      jurisdiction - Optional search condition
      Returns:
      InsuranceCompany entity which can be persisted

    • retrieveInsuranceCompany

      InsuranceCompany retrieveInsuranceCompany(String abUID)
      Retrieve the insurance company entity with the given AddressBookUID from the contact management
      Parameters:
      abUID - The AddressBookUID
      Returns:
      insuranceCompany entity which can be persisted
